pick this thing up

00:38:40.990 --> 00:38:44.910
and very slowly-- the
simulation's a little slow--

00:38:44.910 --> 00:38:50.994
but you can actually drag this
thing out and tie a knot in it.

00:38:50.994 --> 00:38:53.410
Anyway, I think this is going
