00:45:57.280 --> 00:46:00.300
in the survival of the
species side of the camp.

00:46:00.300 --> 00:46:02.609
And so now we have
aerosol cans that

00:46:02.609 --> 00:46:04.150
are much more exciting
than they used

00:46:04.150 --> 00:46:10.180
to be because their propellants
